INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('first.primitive-carrier','Primitive Carrier','primitive-carrier','Reality_Mechanics/1_First/Carrier Mechanics/Primitive Carrier.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/primitive-carrier.html','# Primitive Carrier

Primitive Carrier names the first-order carrier role through which located distinction can be carried as readable relation. Primitive carriers do not engineer or produce distinction. They emerge where bounded asymmetry has become local enough for boundary, placement, presentation, trace, holding, refusal, separation, contrast, or direction to matter.

## Places

Primitive Carrier places the first-order carrier role through which located distinction can be carried as readable relation.

## Holds

Primitive Carrier is held by [[Boundary]] and [[Clearance]]. Distinction must be located while relation remains readable.

## Pairs

Asymmetry carries downward — into [[Operation Carrier]]. Primitive Carrier names the first-order carrier role through which located distinction becomes readable relation. The carrying role flows into its operational form without a lateral co-condition.

## Traces

- [[Boundary]]
- [[Clearance]]

## Nests

Primitive Carrier nests below second-order carrying. It carries located distinction as readable relation without becoming a second-order condition, domain, branch, or engineered operation.

[[Operation Carrier]]
[[Structural Carrier]]

## Reads

Primitive Carrier becomes recognisable where a located distinction can be carried without yet becoming a second-order condition, domain, branch, or engineered operation.

## Carries

- [[Operation Carrier]]
- [[Structural Carrier]]','Primitive Carrier Primitive Carrier names the first order carrier role through which located distinction can be carried as readable relation. Primitive carriers do not engineer or produce distinction. They emerge where bounded asymmetry has become local enough for boundary, placement, presentation, trace, holding, refusal, separation, contrast, or direction to matter. Places Primitive Carrier places the first order carrier role through which located distinction can be carried as readable relation. Holds Primitive Carrier is held by Boundary and Clearance. Distinction must be located while relation remains readable. Pairs Asymmetry carries downward — into Operation Carrier. Primitive Carrier names the first order carrier role through which located distinction becomes readable relation. The carrying role flows into its operational form without a lateral co condition. Traces Boundary Clearance Nests Primitive Carrier nests below second order carrying. It carries located distinction as readable relation without becoming a second order condition, domain, branch, or engineered operation. Operation Carrier Structural Carrier Reads Primitive Carrier becomes recognisable where a located distinction can be carried without yet becoming a second order condition, domain, branch, or engineered operation. Carries Operation Carrier Structural Carrier','Primitive Carrier Primitive Carrier names the first order carrier role through which located distinction can be carried as readable relation. Primitive carriers do not engineer or produce distinction.','stable','rooted',0,'first','class',NULL,'[]','[]','["first.boundary","first.clearance","first.operation-carrier","first.structural-carrier"]','{"holds":["first.boundary","first.clearance"],"traces":["first.boundary","first.clearance"],"carries":["first.operation-carrier","first.structural-carrier"],"pairs":["first.operation-carrier"],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',184,'sha256:98383b37e7b39da2aa5fc3a16d8d9a983ba7937691647b810fcf4f3da48903d6','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('first.read','Read','read','Reality_Mechanics/1_First/Carrier Mechanics/Read.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/read.html','# Read

Read names recognition of meaningful distinction. [[Trace]] makes a distinction followable; read takes that distinction up as meaningful within the current scope. A trace may exist before it is read, and a read may widen or recur without exhausting the trace.

Read enters order; it does not create order. Once entered, read participates in what it traces: it can clarify, distort, repair, accelerate, name, measure, or alter the relation it has entered. The question is whether the read remains traceable and compatible with what carries it.

## Places

Read places recognition of meaningful distinction at the current scope.

## Holds

Read is held by [[Trace]]. The distinction must be followable before it can be taken up as meaningful.

## Pairs

Read is vertical. It names recognition of meaningful distinction and carries this forward into [[Readability]], [[Thread]], [[Step]], and [[Retrace Read|Retrace]]. Read holds [[Trace]]; it is downstream of trace in the carrier chain, not co-present with it as a lateral pair.

## Traces

- [[Trace]]
- [[Attend]]
- [[Hold]]

## Nests

Read nests between trace and readability. It can widen or recur without exhausting the trace.

## Reads

Read becomes recognisable where a traced distinction is taken up as meaningful: the trace is not only followable but significant within the current scope.

Read also becomes recognisable where entry into an already ordered condition changes the relation being read. This makes read a participating condition that must remain answerable to trace.

## Carries

- [[Readability]]
- [[Thread]]
- [[Step]]
- [[Retrace Read|Retrace]]
- [[Consciousness]]
- [[Structural Carrier]]
- [[Communicating]]
- [[Expressing]]
