how fields can be grouped by recurring…','stable','rooted',0,'higher','term',NULL,'[]','[]','["first.relation","first.thread","first.trace","first.visible","ground.seed","higher.hidden-bearing","higher.higher-retrace","higher.invisible-bearing","higher.nested-carrying","higher.web","second.structural-gathering","second.surface","third.field-relationships"]','{"holds":["first.thread","third.field-relationships","higher.nested-carrying","higher.invisible-bearing","second.surface","first.trace"],"traces":["first.thread","third.field-relationships","higher.nested-carrying","higher.invisible-bearing","second.surface","first.trace","second.structural-gathering"],"carries":["higher.hidden-bearing","higher.higher-retrace","higher.web"],"pairs":["higher.web"],"nests":[],"reads":["first.thread","first.visible","ground.seed","first.relation"]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',280,'sha256:2020687a4fc287a6bd8e0c7d07c98309327c13b675eb92a82769a078611ca5ec','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('higher.hidden-bearing','Hidden Bearing','hidden-bearing','Reality_Mechanics/5_Higher/Hidden Bearing.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/hidden-bearing.html','# Hidden Bearing

Hidden Bearing names carrying deliberately structured not to present the dependency path. The carrier holds what is operative but does not surface it in the current read.

Hidden Bearing is the engineered mode of non-presenting carrying.

A parent stepping back to allow a child to struggle through a problem is carrying the child''s development through hidden bearing: the support, the watching, the held readiness to intervene — all active, all structured, none of it surfaced. The hiding is the structurally correct move. Surfacing the bearing would undermine what the bearing is there to carry.

The disorder is not in the hiding. It is in the carrier losing account of how the hidden bearing affects their own carrying. If the sustained readiness is not accounted for, it accumulates and begins to carry the carrier in ways they cannot retrace. That is [[Source Drift]]: hidden bearing going unaccounted for.

[[Invisible Bearing]] becomes non-presenting through organic accumulation. Hidden Bearing is designed: the carrier makes a structural decision not to surface the dependency path. This is the organic/engineered distinction at the higher order level.

## Places

Hidden Bearing places carrying deliberately structured not to present the dependency path — where the carrier holds the bearing but does not surface it in the current read.

## Holds

Hidden Bearing is held by [[Bearing]] and [[Higher Retrace|Retrace]]. Bearing must be operative before it can be deliberately structured not to present, and retrace must be available in principle before its deliberate withholding can be named.

## Pairs

Hidden Bearing pairs with [[Invisible Bearing]]. Invisible Bearing names carrying that becomes non-presenting through organic accumulation; Hidden Bearing names carrying deliberately structured not to present.

## Traces

- [[Bearing]]
- [[Higher Retrace|Retrace]]
- [[Fabric]]
- [[Organic and Organised Organisation]]
- [[Organised Domain]]

## Nests

Hidden Bearing nests where bearing is deliberately held back from presentation — where the carrier holds the dependency and the current read does not surface it.

## Reads

Hidden Bearing becomes recognisable where the carrier holds the dependency path and does not surface it because non-presentation is the structurally correct move.

It is read in parenting, teaching, facilitation, institutional design, and therapeutic practice: anywhere that surfacing the bearing would undermine what the bearing is there to carry. What requires accounting is the effect of hidden bearing on the carrier''s own structure.

[[Source Drift]] is what Hidden Bearing becomes when the carrier stops accounting for what the hidden bearing is doing to them — when the structure of deliberate non-presentation begins to carry the carrier without being traced.

## Carries

- [[Source Drift]]','Hidden Bearing Hidden Bearing names carrying deliberately structured not to present the dependency path. The carrier holds what is operative but does not surface it in the current read. Hidden Bearing is the engineered mode of non presenting carrying. A parent stepping back to allow a child to struggle through a problem is carrying the child''s development through hidden bearing: the support, the watching, the held readiness to intervene — all active, all structured, none of it surfaced. The hiding is the structurally correct move. Surfacing the bearing would undermine what the bearing is there to carry. The disorder is not in the hiding. It is in the carrier losing account of how the hidden bearing affects their own carrying. If the sustained readiness is not accounted for, it accumulates and begins to carry the carrier in ways they cannot retrace. That is Source Drift: hidden bearing going unaccounted for. Invisible Bearing becomes non presenting through organic accumulation. Hidden Bearing is designed: the carrier makes a structural decision not to surface the dependency path. This is the organic/engineered distinction at the higher order level. Places Hidden Bearing places carrying deliberately structured not to present the dependency path — where the carrier holds the bearing but does not surface it in the current read. Holds Hidden Bearing is held by Bearing and Higher Retrace. Bearing must be operative before it can be deliberately structured not to present, and retrace must be available in principle before its deliberate withholding can be named. Pairs Hidden Bearing pairs with Invisible Bearing. Invisible Bearing names carrying that becomes non presenting through organic accumulation; Hidden Bearing names carrying deliberately structured not to present. Traces Bearing Higher Retrace Fabric Organic and Organised Organisation Organised Domain Nests Hidden Bearing nests where bearing is deliberately held back from presentation — where the 