 places, and Resolution Rate tests whether meaningful distinction can resolve without losing order. Carries Atlas Practice','The Working Postulate Reality Mechanics does not begin by defining reality. It begins from a working postulate: These are not final definitions.','stable','rooted',0,'practice','theory',NULL,'["Theory"]','[]','["first.relation","first.trace","ground.root-order","practice.atlas","practice.atlas-practice","practice.posture-read","second.resolution-rate"]','{"holds":["practice.atlas","first.relation","ground.root-order","first.trace"],"traces":["practice.atlas","first.relation","ground.root-order","first.trace"],"carries":["practice.atlas-practice"],"pairs":["practice.atlas"],"nests":[],"reads":["second.resolution-rate","practice.posture-read"]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Claim","anchor":"claim"},{"depth":2,"text":"Status","anchor":"status"},{"depth":2,"text":"Terms As Operations","anchor":"terms-as-operations"},{"depth":2,"text":"Representation Condition","anchor":"representation-condition"},{"depth":2,"text":"Consequence 1: Relation Grounds","anchor":"consequence-1-relation-grounds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Consequence 2: Connection","anchor":"consequence-2-connection"},{"depth":2,"text":"Consequence 3: Carry And Trace","anchor":"consequence-3-carry-and-trace"},{"depth":2,"text":"Consequence 4: Hold, Carry, Place As First-Order Terms","anchor":"consequence-4-hold-carry-place-as-first-order-terms"},{"depth":2,"text":"Consequence 5: Order, Resolution Rate, And Crossings","anchor":"consequence-5-order-resolution-rate-and-crossings"},{"depth":2,"text":"Rules Of Use","anchor":"rules-of-use"},{"depth":2,"text":"Garden Care","anchor":"garden-care"},{"depth":2,"text":"Failure Tests","anchor":"failure-tests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Formal Sketch","anchor":"formal-sketch"},{"depth":2,"text":"Worked Reads","anchor":"worked-reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Relation To Existing Mathematics","anchor":"relation-to-existing-mathematics"},{"depth":2,"text":"Open Problems","anchor"