hat speed is carried by hidden drawdown of attention, labour, energy, trust, or Earth systems, it can also be read through Extractive Acceleration. Carries AI Coupling AI Availability AI Atlas Grounding AI Drift Ungrounded Fabrication AI Misrepair AI Reply Drift AI Confident Correction','AI AI names the third order domain where engineered coupling between generated output, model interface, and human evaluation mediates relation while requiring retraceable dependency. AI can…','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','ai','[]','[]','["second.medium","third.ai-atlas-grounding","third.ai-availability","third.ai-confident-correction","third.ai-coupling","third.ai-drift","third.ai-misrepair","third.ai-reply-drift","third.branch","third.engineered-coupling","third.technology-domain","third.ungrounded-fabrication"]','{"holds":["third.branch","third.engineered-coupling","third.technology-domain","second.medium"],"traces":["third.branch","third.engineered-coupling","third.technology-domain","second.medium"],"carries":["third.ai-coupling","third.ai-availability","third.ai-atlas-grounding","third.ai-drift","third.ungrounded-fabrication","third.ai-misrepair","third.ai-reply-drift","third.ai-confident-correction"],"pairs":[],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',323,'sha256:23a041691d8cf9d34b013ff0cdf21955e8fba0759fd1532f23d2248cab758cce','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.alive','Alive','alive','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Life/Alive.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/alive.html','# Alive

Alive names a life path read where living coupling remains live enough to maintain, repair, adapt, respond, or continue at a closure scope.

This note places [[Live]] inside [[Life]] as living continuation rather than general liveness.

## Places

Alive places the condition through which coupled carrying is sustained through recursive regulation — a living condition that persists by continuing to regulate its own carrying.

## Holds

Alive is held by [[Life]], [[Live]], [[Coupling]], [[Carrying]], [[Recursive Regulation]], [[Compatibility]], and [[Adaptation]]. Coupling must hold, recursive regulation must sustain compatible carrying, and adaptation must remain possible before the condition can be named as alive.

## Pairs

Alive pairs with [[Cancer]]. Alive names the living condition sustained through compatible recursive regulation; Cancer names the disorder where misrepair misdirects re-bearing within that same condition. Each requires the other to be distinguishable at this scope.

## Traces

- [[Life]]
- [[Live]]
- [[Coupling]]
- [[Carrying]]
- [[Recursive Regulation]]
- [[Compatibility]]
- [[Adaptation]]

## Nests

Alive nests within the Life Field as the condition through which recursive regulation sustains coupled carrying — the structural ground for cancer and over-treatment reads.

## Reads

Alive becomes readable where living coupling can still maintain, repair, adapt, respond, resume, or continue compatible carrying at the evaluated scope.

Alive depends on adaptation in this structural sense: local resolutions may complete, but the living condition can still re-enter, reorient, repair, or continue without treating the larger asymmetry as finished.

The dependency movement is:

First: [[Bearing]] holds available relation.

Second: [[Live]], [[Coupling]], [[Carrying]], [[Recursive Regulation]], and [[Compatibility]] make living continuation evaluable at a [[Closure Scope]].

Third: [[Alive]] places that structural read inside [[Life]].

Distinction:

A live condition may not be alive.

An alive condition must remain live somewhere, but may not be outwardly active at every scope.

## Carries

Alive carries [[Cancer]] — the disorder where misrepair misdirects re-bearing within the living condition.

