INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.cognitive-carrying','Cognitive Carrying','cognitive-carrying','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Cognition/Cognitive Carrying.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/cognitive-carrying.html','# Cognitive Carrying

Cognitive carrying names the Bearing participation required to keep information available for use.

## Places

Cognitive Carrying places the condition through which a cognitive state — thought, orientation, or pattern — is continued through participation rather than discharged or discarded.

## Holds

Cognitive Carrying is held by [[Cognition]], [[Bearing]], [[Carrying]], and [[Compatibility]]. Cognition must be present and bearing must hold a cognitive condition before its continuation through participation can be named.

## Pairs

Cognitive Carrying pairs with [[Cognitive Reads]]: cognitive carrying names the condition through which a cognitive state is continued through participation; cognitive reads names the path reads through which thought and memory become evaluable at a closure scope. Each requires the other — carrying presupposes reads through which what is carried can be evaluated; reads presuppose something being carried through participation.

## Traces

- [[Cognition]]
- [[Bearing]]
- [[Carrying]]
- [[Compatibility]]

## Nests

Cognitive Carrying nests within the Cognition Field as the condition through which cognitive states are sustained and carried through participation.

## Reads

Cognitive Carrying becomes readable where information or a read remains available for use across a cognitive condition without becoming incompatible with the dependency path that carries it.

The dependency movement is:

First: [[Bearing]] holds available information.

Second: [[Carrying]] and [[Compatibility]] make that information usable across a cognitive condition.

Third: [[Cognitive Carrying]] places that structural read inside cognition.

## Carries

This note carries no further public branch at this scope.','Cognitive Carrying Cognitive carrying names the Bearing participation required to keep information available for use. Places Cognitive Carrying places the condition through which a cognitive state — thought, orientation, or pattern — is continued through participation rather than discharged or discarded. Holds Cognitive Carrying is held by Cognition, Bearing, Carrying, and Compatibility. Cognition must be present and bearing must hold a cognitive condition before its continuation through participation can be named. Pairs Cognitive Carrying pairs with Cognitive Reads: cognitive carrying names the condition through which a cognitive state is continued through participation; cognitive reads names the path reads through which thought and memory become evaluable at a closure scope. Each requires the other — carrying presupposes reads through which what is carried can be evaluated; reads presuppose something being carried through participation. Traces Cognition Bearing Carrying Compatibility Nests Cognitive Carrying nests within the Cognition Field as the condition through which cognitive states are sustained and carried through participation. Reads Cognitive Carrying becomes readable where information or a read remains available for use across a cognitive condition without becoming incompatible with the dependency path that carries it. The dependency movement is: First: Bearing holds available information. Second: Carrying and Compatibility make that information usable across a cognitive condition. Third: Cognitive Carrying places that structural read inside cognition. Carries This note carries no further public branch at this scope.','Cognitive Carrying Cognitive carrying names the Bearing participation required to keep information available for use. Places Cognitive Carrying places the condition through which a cognitive state…','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','cognition','[]','[]','["first.bearing","second.carrying","second.compatibility","third.cognition","third.cognitive-reads"]','{"holds":["third.cognition","first.bearing","second.carrying","second.compatibility"],"traces":["third.cognition","first.bearing","second.carrying","second.compatibility"],"carries":[],"pairs":["third.cognitive-reads"],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',227,'sha256:d7044be0dcbeba68006fcd967a2ee2ea5ebc7e4ba61ffc47d1adcfba823c0c4e','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.cognitive-metabolism','Cognitive Metabolism','cognitive-metabolism','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Cognition/Cognitive Metabolism.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/cognitive-metabolism.html','# Cognitive Metabolism

Cognitive Metabolism names a resolution pathway where energy, strain, attention, and stimulation are converted primarily through thought, mapping, design, language, prediction, or conceptual ordering.

The traceable question is not whether a person thinks too much. The traceable question is whether thought remains coupled to the organism that carries it.

## Places

Cognitive Metabolism places the cognitive resolution pathway through which strain, attention, stimulation, and available energy are converted through thought, mapping, design, language, prediction, or conceptual ordering.

## Holds

Cognitive Metabolism is held by [[Cognition]], [[Thought]], [[Metabolism]], [[Body]], [[Coupling]], and [[Reality Check]]. Cognition and thought must be present, and thought must remain coupled to the body that carries it, before cognitive metabolism can remain reality-bearing.

## Pairs

No lateral pair is required at this placement yet. Cognitive Metabolism currently reads as a cognitive resolution pathway whose compatibility must still be checked through body, rest, relation, and reality. [[Fatigue]] may reveal where cognitive resolution has exceeded what can be carried, but it is not the structural pair of this term.

## Traces

- [[Cognition]]
- [[Thought]]
- [[Metabolism]]
- [[Body]]
- [[Coupling]]
- [[Reality Check]]

## Nests

Cognitive Metabolism nests within the Cognition Field as a metabolic pathway of embodied cognition, not as escape from the body.

## Reads

Cognitive Metabolism becomes readable where thought, mapping, design, language, prediction, or ordering resolves strain and attention while remaining coupled to body, rest, relation, and reality.

Some minds are not escaping the body. They are one of the body''s most developed metabolic organs. This does not mean thought replaces sleep, repair, movement, nourishment, or relation. It means thought can be one of the body''s main ways of resolving available strain and energy.

Failure appears when thought continues after losing feedback from the body, relation, rest, or reality. Healthy cognitive metabolism remains answerable to the organism and world that carry it.

## Carries

