th":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',180,'sha256:4d3bd56abac6541606434d5f4a75d79f140836f59d8fa5b3a1640bc5c2420b3f','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.expression-field','Expression Field','expression-field','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Expression/Expression Field.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/expression-field.html','# Expression Field

Expression Field names the recurring field of participation through which gesture, making visible, and communicating through form become readable as organised experience.

## Places

Expression Field places a recurring field of participation.

## Holds

Expression Field is held by [[Field of Participation]], [[Organic Field]], [[Expression]], [[Relation]], and [[Medium]]. Field of Participation must structure a recurring scope and relation must be present through a medium before the expression field can be named.

## Pairs

Expression Field pairs with [[Language Field]]: expression field names the field of outward appearance through medium — where relation becomes visibly present through gesture, form, affect, sound, or image; language field names the field of readable difference through medium — where distinction becomes nameable and traceable. Each requires the other to be locatable: expression is only outward against a background of what can be named; language is only readable against a background of expression.

## Traces

- [[Field of Participation]]
- [[Organic Field]]
- [[Expression]]
- [[Relation]]
- [[Medium]]

## Nests

Expression Field nests as a public field container. Detailed branch notes remain compressed as working material.

[[Expression]]
[[Gesture]]
[[Music]]

## Reads

Expression Field becomes recognisable where relation becomes outwardly readable through gesture, form, affect, sound, image, or visible presentation.

At the [[Translation Boundary]], [[Visible]], [[Medium]], [[Pattern]], [[Rhythm]], [[Gesture]], and [[Relation Read]] can become terminal to this field as local reads such as [[Expression]], [[Gesture]], and [[Music]].

## Carries

