Field Relationships names a working grouping of third-order fields by recurring participation emphasis.

## Places

Field Relationships places a working grouping of third-order fields by recurring participation emphasis.

## Holds

Field Relationships is held by [[Third Order]], [[Field of Participation]], and [[Organic Field]].

## Pairs

Field Relationships pairs with [[Field Bearing]]. Field Relationships names how fields bear on each other; Field Bearing names how a field bears through its own conditions. Each is a distinct structural condition at the field level.

## Traces

