obligated. The relational conditions that Law formalises — Civil, Consent and Violation,…','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','society','[]','[]','["first.boundary","third.civil","third.competence-boundary","third.consent","third.constrained-resolution","third.destination-led-carrying","third.repair","third.society-field","third.thin-carrying","third.violation"]','{"holds":["third.society-field","third.civil","third.consent","third.violation","third.repair","first.boundary","third.constrained-resolution","third.competence-boundary","third.destination-led-carrying","third.thin-carrying"],"traces":["third.society-field","third.civil","third.consent","third.violation","third.repair","first.boundary","third.constrained-resolution","third.competence-boundary","third.destination-led-carrying","third.thin-carrying"],"carries":[],"pairs":[],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',779,'sha256:ca9af617496c82f87faacebf31be9ec477a789b3dcb3ee3d8bb2dfa966948082','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.learning-pace','Learning Pace','learning-pace','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Domains/Teaching/Learning Pace.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/learning-pace.html','# Learning Pace

Learning pace names how learning participation remains compatibly carried through a teaching condition without exceeding available bearing.

## Places

Learning Pace places how learning participation remains compatibly carried through a teaching condition without exceeding available bearing.

## Holds

Learning Pace is held by [[Teaching]], [[Bearing]], [[Carrying]], [[Tempo]], [[Pace]].

## Pairs

Learning Pace pairs with [[Teaching Boundary]]. Learning Pace names the supportable rate at which bearing can be received; Teaching Boundary names the edge where that rate can no longer hold.

## Traces

- [[Teaching]]
- [[Bearing]]
- [[Carrying]]
- [[Tempo]]
- [[Pace]]

## Nests

Learning Pace nests where this read holds at its field, domain, or practice scope without losing trace.

## Reads

Learning Pace becomes readable where instruction proceeds at a rate the learner can still carry, test, and re-enter.

The dependency movement is:

First: [[Bearing]] holds learning availability.

Second: [[Carrying]] and [[Compatibility]] make pace evaluable through learner uptake rather than teacher momentum.

Third: [[Learning Pace]] places that structural read inside teaching.

## Carries

