INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.life-field','Life Field','life-field','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Life/Life Field.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/life-field.html','# Life Field

Life Field names the recurring field of participation through which living, biological continuation, growth, and death become readable as organised experience.

## Places

Life Field places a recurring field of participation.

## Holds

Life Field is held by [[Field of Participation]], [[Organic Field]], [[Life]], [[Natural Order]], [[Coupling]], [[Carrying]], and [[Recursive Regulation]]. Field of Participation must structure a recurring scope and natural-order coupling must sustain recursive regulation before the life field can be named.

## Pairs

Life Field pairs with [[Sustenance Field]]. Life Field names the field of living carrying sustained through recursive regulation; Sustenance Field names the field of renewed availability that keeps living carrying possible. Each requires the other: living carrying requires sustenance to continue; sustenance is only sustenance where it renews a living condition.

## Traces

- [[Field of Participation]]
- [[Organic Field]]
- [[Life]]
- [[Natural Order]]
- [[Coupling]]
- [[Carrying]]
- [[Recursive Regulation]]

## Nests

Life Field nests as a public field container. Detailed branch notes remain compressed as working material.

[[Alive]]
[[Cancer]]
[[Life]]
[[Over-Treatment]]
[[Timescale]]

## Reads

Life Field becomes recognisable where living continuation, growth, reproduction, illness, death, or biological carrying organises participation as life.

At the [[Translation Boundary]], [[Live]], [[Growth]], [[Carrying]], [[Recurrence]], [[Timescale]], and [[Resolution]] can become terminal to this field as local reads such as [[Alive]], [[Life]], [[Cancer]], and [[Over-Treatment]].

## Carries

Life Field carries [[Cancer]] and [[Timescale]] as grounded reads at this field scope. Nested reads are recorded under Nests; each traces its own structural ground.

- [[Cancer]]
