econd: Carrying, Recurrence, and Readability make that read returnable. Third: Memory places returnable carried read inside Cognition Field. Higher Order Edge: Memory remains third order where it names returnable carried read. It crosses into higher order where Consciousness, Recursion, or Higher Learning changes how memory is carried, corrected, or used to alter future participation. Movement: Carries Learning Higher Learning','Memory Memory names returnable carried read inside cognition. Storage can carry memory, but storage alone may preserve information without preserving the bearing path that made the read matter.','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','cognition','[]','[]','["higher.higher-learning","second.carrying","second.recurrence","second.retrace-read","third.cognition","third.learning","third.thought"]','{"holds":["third.cognition","third.thought","second.recurrence","second.carrying","second.retrace-read"],"traces":["third.cognition","third.thought","second.recurrence","second.carrying","second.retrace-read"],"carries":["third.learning","higher.higher-learning"],"pairs":["third.thought"],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',340,'sha256:c9b5971f17c75813510aafb0264104cdfa29e64ff1b67160144b6e4c363c6715','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.metabolism','Metabolism','metabolism','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Body/Metabolism.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/metabolism.html','# Metabolism

Metabolism names embodied resolution: the way a living system carries change without losing continuity.

Metabolism is not only calorie-burning or digestion in this Atlas placement. It names the living resolution pattern through which intake, energy, strain, repair, waste, memory, and activity are converted into continued participation.

## Places

Metabolism places embodied resolution within living participation — the way intake, energy, strain, repair, waste, memory, and activity are converted into continued participation.

## Holds

Metabolism is held by [[Body]], [[Life]], [[Intake]], [[Energy]], [[Resolution]], [[Repair]], and [[Participation]]. Living embodied participation must be present, and intake, energy, and repair must be available, before metabolism can be named as embodied resolution.

## Pairs

No lateral pair is required at this placement yet. Metabolism currently reads as the embodied resolution pattern through which living participation continues.

## Traces

- [[Body]]
- [[Life]]
- [[Intake]]
- [[Energy]]
- [[Resolution]]
- [[Repair]]
- [[Participation]]

## Nests

Metabolism nests within the Body Field as the living resolution pathway through which a body carries change without losing continuity.

## Reads

Metabolism becomes readable where a living system converts intake, strain, energy, rest, repair, waste, and activity into continued participation at a particular rate and pattern.

Different living systems resolve at different metabolic rates and patterns. A small bird, a tree, a human body, and a damaged body do not carry change in the same way. Metabolism names the rate and manner of resolution, not a simple measure of efficiency.

In humans, metabolism can include movement, thought, language, craft, emotion, relation, repair, rest, and care as pathways through which available strain and energy are resolved. The traceable question is whether the living carrier remains nourished, repairable, and compatibly coupled to what it is resolving.

## Carries

- [[Cognitive Metabolism]]','Metabolism Metabolism names embodied resolution: the way a living system carries change without losing continuity. Metabolism is not only calorie burning or digestion in this Atlas placement. It names the living resolution pattern through which intake, energy, strain, repair, waste, memory, and activity are converted into continued participation. Places Metabolism places embodied resolution within living participation — the way intake, energy, strain, repair, waste, memory, and activity are converted into continued participation. Holds Metabolism is held by Body, Life, Intake, Energy, Resolution, Repair, and Participation. Living embodied participation must be present, and intake, energy, and repair must be available, before metabolism can be named as embodied resolution. Pairs No lateral pair is required at this placement yet. Metabolism currently reads as the embodied resolution pattern through which living participation continues. Traces Body Life Intake Energy Resolution Repair Participation Nests Metabolism nests within the Body Field as the living resolution pathway through which a body carries change without losing continuity. Reads Metabolism becomes readable where a living system converts intake, strain, energy, rest, repair, waste, and activity into continued participation at a particular rate and pattern. Different living systems resolve at different metabolic rates and patterns. A small bird, a tree, a human body, and a damaged body do not carry change in the same way. Metabolism names the rate and manner of resolution, not a simple measure of efficiency. In humans, metabolism can include movement, thought, language, craft, emotion, relation, repair, rest, and care as pathways through which available strain and energy are resolved. The traceable question is whether the living carrier remains nourished, repairable, and compatibly coupled to what it is resolving. Carries Cognitive Metabolism','Metabolism Metabolism names embodied resolution: the way a living system carries change without losing continuity. Metabolism is not only calorie burning or digestion in this Atlas placement.','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','body','[]','[]','["first.resolution","second.energy","second.intake","second.participation","third.body","third.cognitive-metabolism","third.life","third.repair"]','{"holds":["third.body","third.life","second.intake","second.energy","first.resolution","third.repair","second.participation"],"traces":["third.body","third.life","second.intake","second.energy","first.resolution","third.repair","second.participation"],"carries":["third.cognitive-metabolism"],"pairs":[],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',276,'sha256:0bf023f1940521b8873b1c9cd18f34b11b1f708ac024fd8bbf94a45955318f46','1970-01-01','2026-06-27');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.misrepair','Misrepair','misrepair','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Relational Participation/Bearing Relations/Misrepair.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/misrepair.html','# Misrepair

Misrepair names repair-like continuation that preserves proceeding while carrying the wrong condition.

## Places

Misrepair places repair-like continuation that preserves proceeding while carrying the wrong condition — carrying that appears to repair while failing to restore compatible bearing.

## Holds

Misrepair is held by [[Repair]] and [[Carrying]]. The repair condition must be in view and carrying must continue before proceeding that miscarries repair can be named.

## Pairs

No lateral pair is required at this placement yet; this term currently reads as a branch or terminal read.

## Traces

- [[Repair]]
- [[Carrying]]

## Nests

Misrepair nests within Relational Participation as the condition through which repair fails while its surface is maintained.

## Reads

Misrepair becomes readable where proceeding continues through a repair-like act while compatible bearing remains unrestored or wrongly carried.

## Carries

- [[Repair Mismatch]]
- [[Surface Patch]]
- [[Apology Without Repair]]

The dependency movement is:

First: [[Bearing]] is absent, interrupted, insufficient, or misdirected.

Second: [[Carrying]] continues while [[Compatibility]] remains unrestored.

Third: [[Misrepair]] places that structural read inside bearing relations as repair-like continuation carrying the wrong condition.','Misrepair Misrepair names repair like continuation that preserves proceeding while carrying the wrong condition. Places Misrepair places repair like continuation that preserves proceeding while carrying the wrong condition — carrying that appears to repair while failing to restore compatible bearing. Holds Misrepair is held by Repair and Carrying. The repair condition must be in view and carrying must continue before proceeding that miscarries repair can be named. Pairs No lateral pair is required at this placement yet; this term currently reads as a branch or terminal read. Traces Repair Carrying Nests Misrepair nests within Relational Participation as the condition through which repair fails while its surface is maintained. Reads Misrepair becomes readable where proceeding continues through a repair like act while compatible bearing remains unrestored or wrongly carried. Carries Repair Mismatch Surface Patch Apology Without Repair The dependency movement is: First: Bearing is absent, interrupted, insufficient, or misdirected. Second: Carrying continues while Compatibility remains unrestored. Third: Misrepair places that structural read inside bearing relations as repair like continuation carrying the wrong condition.','Misrepair Misrepair names repair like continuation that preserves proceeding while carrying the wrong condition. Places Misrepair places repair like continuation that preserves proceeding while…','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','relational-participation','[]','[]','["second.carrying","third.apology-without-repair","third.repair","third.repair-mismatch","third.surface-patch"]','{"holds":["third.repair","second.carrying"],"traces":["third.repair","second.carrying"],"carries":["third.repair-mismatch","third.surface-patch","third.apology-without-repair"],"pairs":[],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',172,'sha256:1b285b6d81632bd5e4adb08a046793ffe6bb775b272428528bd1d6fe70043f27','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.modelling','Modelling','modelling','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Fields/Knowledge/Modelling.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/modelling.html','# Modelling

Modelling names a knowledge path read where a condition is carried as a usable representation for evaluation or future participation.

This note places modelling inside the [[Knowledge Field]] as a path read.

## Places

Modelling places the condition through which a read, pattern, or form is carried in a medium as a representation — carrying that makes what is read available to recognition without requiring its direct presence.

## Holds

Modelling is held by [[Knowledge Field]], [[Read]], [[Recognition Read|Recognition]], [[Pattern]], [[Medium]], and [[Form]]. A read must be present, a pattern must be recognisable, and a medium must carry the form before representation as modelling can be named.

## Pairs

Modelling pairs with [[Competence Boundary]]. Modelling names the representation through which compatible carrying is extended through medium; Competence Boundary names the located scope at which that carrying can no longer be reliably extended. Each requires the other: modelling extends what competence boundary marks as the limit.

## Traces

- [[Knowledge Field]]
- [[Read]]
- [[Recognition Read|Recognition]]
- [[Pattern]]
- [[Medium]]
- [[Form]]

- [[Knowledge]]
## Nests

Modelling nests within the Knowledge Field as the path read for carried representation — the structural ground for AI, externalised cognition, and knowledge-system reads.

## Reads

Modelling becomes readable where a condition is carried in a simplified or usable form without becoming the condition itself.

The dependency movement is:

First: [[Boundary]] and [[Availability]] make a condition present enough to be modelled.

Second: [[Read]], [[Recognition Read|Recognition]], [[Pattern]], [[Medium]], [[Form]], and [[Closure Scope]] make the carried model evaluable.

Third: [[Modelling]] places that carried read in the [[Knowledge Field]] as a path read.

## Carries

This note carries no further public branch at this scope.','Modelling Modelling names a knowledge path read where a condition is carried as a usable representation for evaluation or future participation. This note places modelling inside the Knowledge Field as a path read. Places Modelling places the condition through which a read, pattern, or form is carried in a medium as a representation — carrying that makes what is read available to recognition without requiring its direct presence. Holds Modelling is held by Knowledge Field, Read, Recognition Read, Pattern, Medium, and Form. A read must be present, a pattern must be recognisable, and a medium must carry the form before representation as modelling can be named. Pairs Modelling pairs with Competence Boundary. Modelling names the representation through which compatible carrying is extended through medium; Competence Boundary names the located scope at which that carrying can no longer be reliably extended. Each requires the other: modelling extends what competence boundary marks as the limit. Traces Knowledge Field Read Recognition Read Pattern Medium Form Knowledge Nests Modelling nests within the Knowledge Field as the path read for carried representation — the structural ground for AI, externalised cognition, and knowledge system reads. Reads Modelling becomes readable where a condition is carried in a simplified or usable form without becoming the condition itself. The dependency movement is: First: Boundary and Availability make a condition present enough to be modelled. Second: Read, Recognition Read, Pattern, Medium, Form, and Closure Scope make the carried model evaluable. Third: Modelling places that carried read in the Knowledge Field as a path read. Carries This note carries no further public branch at this scope.','Modelling Modelling names a knowledge path read where a condition is carried as a usable representation for evaluation or future participation. This note places modelling inside the Knowledge…','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','knowledge','[]','[]','["first.read","second.form","second.medium","second.pattern","second.recognition-read","third.competence-boundary","third.knowledge","third.knowledge-field"]','{"holds":["third.knowledge-field","first.read","second.recognition-read","second.pattern","second.medium","second.form"],"traces":["third.knowledge-field","first.read","second.recognition-read","second.pattern","second.medium","second.form","third.knowledge"],"carries":[],"pairs":["third.competence-boundary"],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","anchor":"pairs"},{"depth":2,"text":"Traces","anchor":"traces"},{"depth":2,"text":"Nests","anchor":"nests"},{"depth":2,"text":"Reads","anchor":"reads"},{"depth":2,"text":"Carries","anchor":"carries"}]',265,'sha256:ae537028a17ff67d017823b31bf1739df19dd0af0b57974eaae44f7f6e4692e2','1970-01-01','2026-06-25');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO entries (id,title,slug,source_path,public_url,content,plain_text,excerpt,status,garden_status,grounded,entry_order,entry_type,branch,aliases,tags,related,structure,headings,word_count,content_hash,created,updated) VALUES ('third.moving','Moving','moving','Reality_Mechanics/3_Third/Placement Modes/Moving.md','https://atlas.realitymechanics.nz/moving.html','# Moving

Moving names the placement mode where participation is primarily carried through traversal, change of position, action, or directional proceeding.

## Places

Moving places the mode where participation is primarily carried through traversal, change of position, or directional proceeding — where what is carried moves through a route rather than staying situated.

## Holds

Moving is held by [[Placement Mode]], [[Traversal]], [[Proceed]], and [[Carrying]]. A mode of participation must exist, traversal must be available, a direction of proceeding must be readable, and carrying must persist before change of position can be placed as the primary mode.

## Pairs

Moving pairs with [[Locating]]. Locating names where something is positioned; Moving names the traversal through which that position changes.

## Traces

- [[Placement Mode]]
- [[Traversal]]
- [[Proceed]]
- [[Carrying]]

## Nests

Moving nests within Placement Modes as the traversal mode — where the primary movement is participation changing location, path, or action through a carried route.

## Reads

Moving becomes recognisable where a note is primarily placed by participation changing location, state, path, posture, or action through a carried route.

## Carries

This note carries no further public branch at this scope.','Moving Moving names the placement mode where participation is primarily carried through traversal, change of position, action, or directional proceeding. Places Moving places the mode where participation is primarily carried through traversal, change of position, or directional proceeding — where what is carried moves through a route rather than staying situated. Holds Moving is held by Placement Mode, Traversal, Proceed, and Carrying. A mode of participation must exist, traversal must be available, a direction of proceeding must be readable, and carrying must persist before change of position can be placed as the primary mode. Pairs Moving pairs with Locating. Locating names where something is positioned; Moving names the traversal through which that position changes. Traces Placement Mode Traversal Proceed Carrying Nests Moving nests within Placement Modes as the traversal mode — where the primary movement is participation changing location, path, or action through a carried route. Reads Moving becomes recognisable where a note is primarily placed by participation changing location, state, path, posture, or action through a carried route. Carries This note carries no further public branch at this scope.','Moving Moving names the placement mode where participation is primarily carried through traversal, change of position, action, or directional proceeding. Places Moving places the mode where…','stable','rooted',0,'third','term','placement-modes','[]','[]','["second.carrying","second.proceed","second.traversal","third.locating","third.placement-mode"]','{"holds":["third.placement-mode","second.traversal","second.proceed","second.carrying"],"traces":["third.placement-mode","second.traversal","second.proceed","second.carrying"],"carries":[],"pairs":["third.locating"],"nests":[],"reads":[]}','[{"depth":2,"text":"Places","anchor":"places"},{"depth":2,"text":"Holds","anchor":"holds"},{"depth":2,"text":"Pairs","