## Reads

Relational Participation Field becomes recognisable where relations between participants become organised enough to be read through care, harm, repair, reciprocity, control, or maintained coupling.
## Carries

Relational Participation Field carries [[Bearing Relations]] and [[Safety]] — the subdomain of coupling and bearing reads, and the condition through which compatible bearing is protected from violation and collapse.
